{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":39,"arguments_yes_count":3,"arguments_no_count":3,"id":205,"created_at":"2015-09-27T21:02:15+0200","updated_at":"2015-09-27T21:02:15+0200","body":"<p><span style=\"line-height:1.6\">1\/ proposer tous les services de l&#39;&eacute;tat sous forme d&#39;API.<\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"line-height:1.6\">2\/ y adjoindre un moteur de recherche interne, transversal et s&eacute;mantique. Ce moteur de recherche devra avoir sa propre API de recherche et d&#39;insertion.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>","versions_count":1,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":6,"author":{"username":"Vincent Pinte Deregnaucourt","displayName":"Vincent Pinte Deregnaucourt","uniqueId":"vincentpintederegnaucourt","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/vincentpintederegnaucourt","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":94,"title":"Section 1","subtitle":"Neutralit\u00e9 de l\u2019internet","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[{"isContribuable":false,"id":5782,"body":"@Laurent Martin: faux, on peut, m\u00eame en laissant les (documentation et codes exemples d')API publiques, contr\u00f4ler qui peut effectivement demander les donn\u00e9es \/ interagir au nom des citoyens, cf les protocoles OAuth et OAuth2 (ils ne sont pas les seuls dans ce cas je pense).","created_at":"2015-10-18T12:31:32+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-18T12:31:32+0200","is_enabled":true,"votes_count":0,"type":1,"is_trashed":false,"author":{"username":"Gami","displayName":"Gami","uniqueId":"gami","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.repu